      "date": "2014-06-09 22:28:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nMore generally we need to figure out why the client is sending empty ACLs in the first place.  Unless we're clearing an existing ACL this is a complete waste of work.  There's no need to send the setxattr request at all.",
